# CLI sidecar 构建产物 (由 scripts/build-cli.sh 生成, 见 app/flowix-desktop/tauri.conf.json externalBin)
app/flowix-desktop/binaries/flowix-cli-*
# dev-mode symlink: Tauri 2 `cargo tauri dev` 找 `binaries/flowix-cli` (无 triple);
# scripts/build-cli.sh 在单 host build 后创建。 永远不 commit 符号链接本身。
app/flowix-desktop/binaries/flowix-cli
app/flowix-desktop/binaries/flowix-cli.exe
!app/flowix-desktop/binaries/.gitkeep

